{"tid":2266760,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「鋼琴女神」李元玲4天暴瘦4公斤！　剩皮包肋骨…網嚇壞：像被虐待","createTime":"2020-11-01T14:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T16:54:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a7985481c4f196eee06dac7eaaff0433c0ae4378","tid":2266760,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞鋼琴家李元玲不只有好琴藝，加上平時熱愛健身運動，練出漂亮體態，還得到「鋼琴女神」的稱號。然而，她最近因為身體不適，竟在短短4天內就暴瘦4公斤，原本結實的腰腹都浮出肋骨形狀，讓粉絲看了大受驚嚇。<br />\n<br />\n李元玲身高高達170公分，但原本就只有46公斤，近期因為生理期到來，不舒服之下幾乎沒有胃口，竟然在4天內一口氣掉到只剩42公斤。她拍下現在的身材，不只皮膚狀態看起來不太好，肋骨線條更是清楚地浮現，幾乎已經是「皮包骨」的健康不良狀態。<br />\n<br />\n看到身體變成這副模樣，李元玲自己也相當無奈，做出對比圖PO在Instagram，自嘲：「Do u see a lot of sadness in the 2nd picture.（你們有在第2張圖中看到滿滿的悲傷嗎）」不少粉絲也吃驚回應「第二張彷彿被家暴虐待」、「看起來很不舒服」、「請保重妳的身體」，希望她趕快回復健康體重。<br />\n<br />\n李元玲曾經當過芭蕾舞者，原本體重為52公斤、體脂量26%，雖然屬於健康範圍，但因為被批評上鏡不好看，從此賣力健身、控制飲食，體重降到46公斤左右，體脂更是只有12%。她嚴格管理自己，天天都健身90分鐘，吃東西則以大量蔬菜和低脂肉類為主，少攝取精緻澱粉和糖分，1個月只允許自己放縱1次，藉此保持理想的身材。"},{"pid":"ff27529beca84f92a5a891a66eeb3ef512691d30","tid":2266760,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5242/d5242573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5242%2Fd5242573.jpg&h=6bb8e3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲4天暴瘦4公斤。（圖／翻攝自李元玲Instagram）"},{"pid":"073272b7fda1453ee4b525a36df00d2a3ec57dd3","tid":2266760,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0c0defa48882fa577a8497985803664fe2819a","tid":2266760,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5242/d5242574.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5242%2Fd5242574.jpg&h=617dead4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲有「鋼琴女神」之稱。（圖／翻攝自李元玲Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5242/d5242576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5242%2Fd5242576.jpg&h=2358eda9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲熱衷健身，原本有著健康的體態。（圖／翻攝自李元玲Instagram）"},{"pid":"849b2332028ba14b786ba01bcc146057699736b2","tid":2266760,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"太肥啦"},{"pid":"00046d46aa4961e307e1f4656fc5a843f09939fe","tid":2266760,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff27529beca84f92a5a891a66eeb3ef512691d30","tid":2266760,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5242/d5242573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5242%2Fd5242573.jpg&h=6bb8e3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李元玲4天暴瘦4公斤。（圖／翻攝自李元玲Instagram）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"嘩屌圖右邊有42 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbfcf49fb928fe743617a32fda82e8063b8f68a","tid":2266760,"uid":149833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"個胸無縮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d177909a4eea389977f2fb6f713ba1cf9652bc95","tid":2266760,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00046d46aa4961e307e1f4656fc5a843f09939fe","tid":2266760,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff27529beca84f92a5a891a66eeb3ef512691d30","tid":2266760,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5242/d5242573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5242%2Fd5242573.jpg&h=6bb8e3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br /